Hello, 

Congratulations. This is a very cool, and beautiful application of=
 evolutionary computation. If you don't mind, I'd like to show portions of =
this video to my Evolutionary Robotics class (and potentially in talks as w=
ell) as a nice application of EC. Would you mind sharing the video file or =
posting it to youtube, where I can use keepvid.com to grab it? I may also b=
e able to use keepvid with a Vimeo link. 

Please also let me know what cit=
e/credit you'd like me to provide when I show it. 

The portion of the vide=
o I am interested in is about 00:18 to 00:57. 

Good luck with your release=
. We're all rooting for your success. 

Best regards,
Jeff Clune
